data.description: Welcome Home ! This home features an upgraded kitchen with quartz counters, oversized breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances which are sure to be a highlight for many buyers. The new laminate wood flooring and freshly painted interior and exterior will also add to the home's appeal. Additionally, the energy-efficient dual pane Aragon gas insulated windows and relatively new roof (just over 10 years old) are great selling points that can help buyers save on energy costs and avoid costly repairs. There are also several fruit trees in the backyard.    Overall, this home is a great opportunity for anyone looking for a move-in ready property with modern upgrades and energy-efficient features. I would encourage anyone interested in this property to schedule an appointment to see it before it is sold.
